{
  "stem": "8892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My aunt-- my aunt holding her little child, who was Eva, too, but she was about 12 or 13-- and some other.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We have to be five, no matter what.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was just 15 minutes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they hollered, don't bring your suitcase.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leave everything there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just come off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they just actually throw us out or grab us and dump us down, you know, from the-- from the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And right away, rails-- as-- you didn't have time to look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But as you looked, you saw thousands of people coming out of that long train.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have no idea who, what, where.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At this point, you just want to be together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the main thing-- holding hands, and the girls, too, holding hands.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] that I remember vividly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "As we arriving and are forming a line, the railroad track gate was sort of in front of us, you know, where we were.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And a German is front of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, of course, he asking everybody how old you are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I definitely would have said 15, which is 15.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, my sister and three Weiss girls, who was about 21, 24, and I think was the oldest, 25, they, they go right there, to the left.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'm holding my mother's hand and facing that gate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a soldier, he would, this second, ask me how old I am.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But a truck was coming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And for split second, he turns around.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I let my mother hand go and run after my sister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Edith, Edith!",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That instinct was with me that I wanted to be with the big girls always, you know, that I want to grow up, whatever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Don't ask me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
